ExpSyntax.val: IF({1,21}, 'mu.ebene1='&Trim(Str({1,5},'3')) &' and mu.ebene2='&Trim(Str({1,6},'3')) &' and mu.ebene3='&Trim(Str({1,7},'3')) &' and mu.ebene4='&Trim(Str({1,8},'3')) &' and ', 'mu.ebene1=lp.ebene1 and mu.ebene2=lp.ebene2 and mu.ebene3=lp.ebene3 and mu.ebene4=lp.ebene4 and ' )

SQL_STMT_U.val: select count (distinct kundennr) as AnzahlKunden from HOTLINE where MitarbeiterNr=:1 and Rufeingang_Datum>=':2' and Rufeingang_Datum<=':3' and Job_beendet=1 and TicketBereich='V' and gesamtdauer>':4' :5
select count (lfd_Job_Nr) from HOTLINE where MitarbeiterNr=:1 and Rufeingang_Datum>=':2' and Rufeingang_Datum<=':3' and Job_beendet=1 and TicketBereich='V' and gesamtdauer>':4' :5

select count (Aktions_Nr) from HOTLINE_AKTION ak inner join HOTLINE hl on (hl.Ebene1=ak.Ebene1 and hl.Ebene2=ak.Ebene2 and hl.Ebene3=ak.Ebene3 and hl.Ebene4=ak.Ebene4 and hl.lfd_Job_Nr=ak.Job_Nr and Job_beendet=1 and TicketBereich='V'and gesamtdauer>':6') where ak.Benutzer=:1 and ak.erstellt_Datum>=':2' and ak.erstellt_Datum<=':3' and ak.erledigt=1 and ak.Folgestatus=':4' :5

select count (Aktions_Nr) from HOTLINE_AKTION ak inner join HOTLINE hl on (hl.Ebene1=ak.Ebene1 and hl.Ebene2=ak.Ebene2 and hl.Ebene3=ak.Ebene3 and hl.Ebene4=ak.Ebene4 and hl.lfd_Job_Nr=ak.Job_Nr and Job_beendet=1 and TicketBereich='V'and gesamtdauer>':8') where ak.Benutzer=:1 and ak.erstellt_Datum>=':2' and ak.erstellt_Datum<=':3' and ak.erledigt=1 and (ak.Folgestatus=':4' or ak.Folgestatus=':5' or ak.Folgestatus=':6') :7

select SUM(cast(substring(hz.Dauer,1,2) as float)+cast(substring(hz.Dauer,3,2) as float)/60+cast(substring(hz.Dauer,5,2) as float)/60/60) as StundenGesamt from HOTLINE_ZEITEN hz inner join HOTLINE hl on (hl.Ebene1=hz.Ebene1 and hl.Ebene2=hz.Ebene2 and hl.Ebene3=hz.Ebene3 and hl.Ebene4=hz.Ebene4 and hl.lfd_Job_Nr=hz.Job_Nr and hl.Job_beendet=1 and hl.TicketBereich='V' and hl.gesamtdauer>':1') where hz.Mitarbeiter_Nr=:2 and hz.datum>=':3' and hz.Datum<=':4' :5

select count (distinct Rufeingang_Datum) as AnzahlTage from HOTLINE where MitarbeiterNr=:1 and Rufeingang_Datum>=':2' and Rufeingang_Datum<=':3' and Job_beendet=1 and TicketBereich='V' and gesamtdauer>':4' :5

select SUM( (cast(substring(lp.Zeit_Logout,1,2) as float)+cast(substring(lp.zeit_logout,3,2) as float)/60+cast(substring(lp.zeit_logout,5,2) as float)/60/60) - (cast(substring(lp.zeit_login,1,2) as float)+cast(substring(lp.zeit_login,3,2) as float)/60+cast(substring(lp.zeit_login,5,2) as float)/60/60)) as Login_Dauer from login_protokoll as lp inner join MITARBEITER_USER mu on (:5 mu.User_Name=lp.Username) where lp.Datum_Login>=':1' and lp.Datum_Login<=':2' and lp.Zeit_Logout>lp.Zeit_Login and mu.Mitarbeiter_Nr=:3 :4
